jovic of yugoslavia told a news conference that the ceasefire 
is operational the situation along the border is generally calm 
some minor problems and questions we are resolving through 
negotiations and enjoying very good help through the understanding 
of both parties jovic said 
he refused to say what the minor problems were but indicated 
there had been no confirmed major violations of the ceasefire that 
took hold aug 20 
