killed an iraqi soldier was unconfirmed but was being 
investigated 
he said the roughly 300 un observers on the ground were in the 
process of determining the positions held by both sides when 
fighting halted in the nearly 8yearold war 
under a plan of action set out by un secretarygeneral javier 
perez de cuellar withdrawal to the prewar border is due at a 
later stage 
defining the border is a key factor in the current peace talks 
between iranian and iraqi leaders 
